719
00:37:12,238 --> 00:37:13,238
Ipasa mo sa akin!

720
00:37:14,198 --> 00:37:16,367
Sabi ko ibalik mo!
naiinis na ako ngayon!

721
00:37:16,784 --> 00:37:18,619
<i>[Nagpapalakpak ang mga lalaki]</i>

722
00:37:20,371 --> 00:37:22,248
Ibigay mo sa akin! Ngayon na!

723
00:37:22,582 --> 00:37:23,707
Sige, ipasa mo! Ipasa ito!

724
00:37:23,708 --> 00:37:24,708
Felix.

725
00:37:27,170 --> 00:37:29,130
sinasabi ko sayo,
Naiinis na talaga ako sayo!

726
00:37:31,007 --> 00:37:33,718
<i>[Nagpapalakpak ang mga lalaki]</i>

727
00:37:34,051 --> 00:37:35,051
Itigil mo na!

728
00:37:35,344 --> 00:37:36,970
Guys, naiinis ako ngayon!

729
00:37:36,971 --> 00:37:38,555
<i>[Nagpapalakpak ang mga lalaki]</i>

730
00:37:38,556 --> 00:37:39,640
Hoy!

731
00:37:39,766 --> 00:37:41,141
Anong ginagawa mo, pare? Hawakan mo siya!

732
00:37:41,142 --> 00:37:42,225
Guys, tigilan niyo na.

733
00:37:42,226 --> 00:37:44,061
Hawakan mo siya, kuya!

734
00:37:44,353 --> 00:37:45,146
Huwag mo siyang pakawalan!

735
00:37:45,147 --> 00:37:47,027
- Anong balak mong gawin?!
- Gawin ito nang mabilis!

736
00:37:48,816 --> 00:37:49,858
Dito na tayo!

737
00:37:49,859 --> 00:37:51,778
Anong gagawin mo sa bag ko?!

738
00:37:58,868 --> 00:38:02,497
Igalang ang bandila! Seksyon E...

739
00:38:03,122 --> 00:38:04,831
saludo...

740
00:38:04,832 --> 00:38:05,832
Ngayon na!

741
00:38:23,851 --> 00:38:25,895
Anong kalokohan ang ginagawa mo?
Ibaba mo ang bag ko!

742
00:38:26,354 --> 00:38:29,315
Huwag maging walang galang.
Iginagalang natin ang watawat.

743
00:38:30,066 --> 00:38:31,484
Haltak! Anong ibig mong sabihing "bandila?!"

744
00:38:31,901 --> 00:38:32,901
Teka.

745
00:38:33,820 --> 00:38:34,820
Teka.

746
00:38:35,071 --> 00:38:36,280
Respeto... ang bag!

747
00:38:39,242 --> 00:38:41,661
Ikaw! Sumasali ka sa saya ha?!

748
00:38:43,830 --> 00:38:46,706
Sinasabi ko sa inyo, guys!
Baka matunaw yung chocolate!

749
00:38:46,707 --> 00:38:47,333
tsokolate?

750
00:38:47,334 --> 00:38:49,251
Hoy! Chocolate ba ang sinabi niya?

751
00:38:49,252 --> 00:38:50,878
Ibaba mo yan! Ibaba mo yan!

752
00:38:53,422 --> 00:38:54,965
Mas mabilis! Kunin mo!

753
00:38:54,966 --> 00:38:56,341
Hoy tsokolate!

754
00:38:56,342 --> 00:38:58,760
- Hoy, Ci-N! pare!
- Ci-N! Ibigay mo sa akin!

755
00:38:58,761 --> 00:39:00,388
- Kunin mo!
- Ibigay mo sa akin!

756
00:39:02,223 --> 00:39:03,099
Hindi! Kunin mo ang bag sa kanya!

757
00:39:03,099 --> 00:39:04,099
Atake!

758
00:39:04,475 --> 00:39:05,475
Mas mabilis!

759
00:39:06,018 --> 00:39:07,018
Habulin mo siya!

760
00:39:08,354 --> 00:39:10,106
- Naiinis na talaga ako!
- Jay-jay!

761
00:39:10,565 --> 00:39:11,565
Jay-jay!

762
00:39:12,608 --> 00:39:13,608
Atake!

763
00:39:14,402 --> 00:39:16,111
- Magmadali!
- Kunin mo siya!

764
00:39:16,112 --> 00:39:17,113
Mas mabilis!

765
00:39:29,625 --> 00:39:31,419
Sa tingin ko oras na para sabihin natin sa mga lalaki.

766
00:39:40,136 --> 00:39:41,136
Keifer!

767
00:39:41,387 --> 00:39:42,054
Anong meron?

768
00:39:42,388 --> 00:39:43,388
Si Jay-jay naman!

769
00:39:44,348 --> 00:39:45,850
Inaaway niya ang mga lalaking nanakit sa kanya!

770
00:39:46,267 --> 00:39:47,518
Huh?! Nasaan sila?!

771
00:40:05,369 --> 00:40:06,787
Mayroon kang ilang lakas ng loob.

772
00:40:08,664 --> 00:40:09,664
Sino ka sa tingin mo?

773
00:40:09,874 --> 00:40:12,585
May message ako kay Freya.
Maaari mo bang ihatid ito?

774
00:40:12,835 --> 00:40:14,235
Kami ang may mensahe para sa iyo.

775
00:40:15,004 --> 00:40:16,004
<i>[nagpupumiglas]</i>

776
00:40:20,217 --> 00:40:22,428
<i>Ano ang ginagawa ng Hari ng mga Assholes dito?</i>

777
00:40:26,015 --> 00:40:27,016
Dude, bumangon ka na!

778
00:41:14,313 --> 00:41:16,022
May announcement sa group chat.

779
00:41:16,023 --> 00:41:17,108
Suspendido ang mga klase!

780
00:41:19,527 --> 00:41:20,361
Dito ka nag-stay?

781
00:41:20,362 --> 00:41:23,322
Yuri, kamag-anak ka ba ni Keifer?
Pareho kayo ng ugali.

782
00:41:24,615 --> 00:41:25,574
Kahit ano.

783
00:41:25,575 --> 00:41:27,076
Bobo na paghahambing.

784
00:41:28,244 --> 00:41:31,997
mamamatay na ako!

785
00:41:31,998 --> 00:41:35,126
Isa, dalawa, tatlo!

786
00:41:39,130 --> 00:41:40,214
saan tayo?

787
00:41:40,506 --> 00:41:43,009
Hindi ito bahay. Ito ay isang gusali!

788
00:41:43,217 --> 00:41:44,801
Ito ba ang iyong tunay na buhok?

789
00:41:44,802 --> 00:41:45,845
Bagay sayo.

790
00:41:46,095 --> 00:41:48,013
Alam mo, binabawi ko ang sinabi ko.

791
00:41:48,014 --> 00:41:49,389
Iba ka kay Keifer.

792
00:41:49,390 --> 00:41:52,351
Mas madali kang lapitan at kausap.

793
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:54,227
Bigla kaming inatake nung babaeng yun!

794
00:41:54,228 --> 00:41:56,104
Sinubukan naming labanan siya,

795
00:41:56,105 --> 00:41:59,108
ngunit dumating si Keifer at ginawa ito sa amin!

796
00:41:59,275 --> 00:42:00,400
Hindi lahat ng sinabi niya ay totoo!

797
00:42:00,401 --> 00:42:01,736
So sinong may kasalanan dito?

798
00:42:01,819 --> 00:42:02,611
Si Keifer yun!

799
00:42:02,820 --> 00:42:04,404
Hindi kasalanan ni Keifer.

800
00:42:04,405 --> 00:42:06,157
Ako ang nagsimula nito.

801
00:42:06,657 --> 00:42:08,534
Paano natin gagamitin
Jay-jay laban kay Aries?

802
00:42:08,784 --> 00:42:10,494
Gagawin ko siya
umibig sa akin.

